				\begin{document}$$11.5 V<V_{bat}<13.5 V$$\end{document}.In this case, we will continue to charge the batteries.
- Mode 2 battery is being charged, it is not between 11.5V<Vbat<13.5V\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
