				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$11.5 V<V_{bat}<13.5 V$$\end{document} but higher than 13.5 V. In this case, the protection system will disconnect the battery by opening S2 and S3 relay.
- Mode 3 The battery is being charged, it is not between11.5V<Vbat<13.5V\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
